# Full Context Rule

When working on this codebase, always read the complete contents of files before making changes. Do not assume file contents from memory or prior conversation context.

Key files to read before any component work:
- `src/App.jsx` (router structure)
- `src/lib/slider.js` (Three.js slider module)
- `src/data/imageImports.js` (image manifest)
- `src/index.css` (all styles)
- `src/translations/index.js` (all bilingual strings)

When editing a component, always read both the component file AND its associated hook and view files.
